{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_001", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "诸葛亮在出山前让童子取来一把羽扇，说此扇日后会派上大用场。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "赤壁之战中诸葛亮用这把羽扇借来了东风，火烧赤壁大败曹军。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_002", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "秦始皇在巡游时遇到一个方士，方士献上了一颗丹药，说能长生不老。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "秦始皇服下丹药后并未长生，而是陷入了假死状态。千年后他在现代苏醒。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_003", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "韩信年轻时在河边遇到一个老婆婆，老婆婆给了他一个锦囊。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "韩信功成名就后打开锦囊，里面写着'功高震主，急流勇退'——可惜他明白得太晚了。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_004", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "李白在长安酒肆中遇到一个神秘的胡人，胡人送了他一把短剑。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "安史之乱爆发时李白用这把短剑自卫，才发现剑中藏着一卷兵书。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_005", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "唐太宗在玄武门之变前夜做了一个梦，梦到一条青龙和一条白虎在争斗。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "青龙代表李世民自己，白虎代表他的兄弟。梦境预示了第二天的血战。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_006", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "郑和的船队中有一艘特殊的船，上面装着大量瓷器，郑和说那是礼物。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "瓷器中藏着一封国书和一份世界地图——是给远方未知国度的友好信物。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_007", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "岳飞在出征前到寺庙求签，主持给了他一个'慎'字。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "岳飞没有听进去，最终以'莫须有'的罪名被处死。'慎'字暗示他需要谨慎行事。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_008", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "朱元璋小时候在皇觉寺扫地时发现了一块刻着字的石碑。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "石碑上记载着'朱氏当兴'的预言，预示了他将来会成为皇帝。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_009", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "司马迁的父亲临终前交给他一卷竹简，嘱咐他一定要完成。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "竹简上是父亲已经搜集的史料，司马迁在此基础上完成了《史记》。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_010", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王昭君出塞前，汉元帝赐了她一把琵琶，说想家了可以弹弹。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "琵琶中藏着一幅汉朝的地图和一份密诏——必要时可打开。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_011", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "曹操在官渡之战前收到一封来自许攸的信，他没打开就烧了。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "许攸本是曹操的好友，因为曹操不信任他而投靠了袁绍。这封信本是警告。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_012", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "张骞出使西域时，汉武帝给了他一个密封的竹筒。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "竹筒中是空白的丝绸，张骞后来在上面绘制了西域各国的地图。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_013", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "武则天还是才人时，一个相士说她'有帝王之相'，被太宗听到了。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "太宗因此疏远了她，但这话最终成真——武则天成了中国唯一的女皇帝。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_014", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "苏轼被贬黄州时在江边捡到一块奇石，上面有天然的纹路。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "纹路看起来像一幅地图。三年后苏轼才明白，那是他人生起落的轨迹图。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_015", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "成吉思汗年幼时，一个路过的喇嘛说他'脚下有七星'。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "七星是成吉思汗一生中最重要的七场战役的象征，每场都改变了历史的走向。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_016", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "崇祯皇帝登基后发现御书房中有一个上锁的抽屉，钥匙却找不到。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "抽屉中是前朝太监留下的密信，揭露了朝中结党营私的名单。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_017", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "戚继光在练兵时发现几个新兵用的兵器上刻着同样的记号。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "那些兵器出自同一个铁匠之手——而那个铁匠是倭寇派来的奸细。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_018", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "康熙微服私访时在客栈墙上看到一首诗，落款是'江南一醉客'。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "诗中含有藏头暗语——'官商勾结，江南有变'。康熙因此提前防范了一场叛乱。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_019", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "左宗棠在出兵新疆前，在祖先牌位前跪了一整夜。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "他是在向祖先发誓——不收复新疆誓不还朝。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_020", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "唐僧从长安出发时，太宗给了他一柄禅杖和一个紫金钵盂。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "low"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "禅杖中空藏着一卷《心经》，是太宗请高僧手抄的护身符。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_021", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王安石变法失败后，在江宁的庭院里种了一棵松树。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "松树是象征——'岁寒然后知松柏之后凋也'，他在等待后人理解他的苦心。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_022", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "杨家将出征前，佘太君交给杨六郎一杆银枪，说是祖传的。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "银枪中藏着一卷兵法和一张阵图，是杨业留下的遗物。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_023", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "李世民在太原起兵前，梦中见到一个白衣人教他剑法。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "白衣人是他的祖先李广的英灵，传授他的剑法后来在战场上救了他的命。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_024", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "文成公主入藏时带了一尊佛像，说是释迦牟尼十二岁等身像。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "佛像的底座中藏有医学和农耕典籍，这是唐王朝送给吐蕃的'知识种子'。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_025", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "海瑞在淳安县做县令时，一个乞丐递给他一张纸条就消失了。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "纸条上写着县里大户人家勾结官府鱼肉百姓的证据。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_026", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "郑成功收复台湾时，部下在一个山洞中发现了一艘明代早期的沉船。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "沉船中满载着瓷器，郑成功用这些瓷器从当地部落手中换来了情报和补给。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_027", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "雍正皇帝在潜邸时养了一只白鹰，称帝后白鹰飞走了。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "白鹰是十四阿哥胤禵送来的——十四阿哥是雍正夺嫡最大的对手。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_028", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "勾践在吴国为奴时，夫差赏了他一把佩剑以示信任。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "勾践用这把剑在二十年后的灭吴之战中亲手斩下了夫差的首级。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_029", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "赵匡胤在陈桥兵变前，一个道士送了他一件黄袍。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "黄袍就是后来被部下披在他身上的那件龙袍——道士早已预见了兵变。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_030", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王阳明在龙场悟道前，在山洞中发现了一本古书，已经被虫蛀了大半。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "古书上只剩下几句话——'心即理也'，这几个字成就了一代心学大师。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_031", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "霍去病在漠北之战前，卫青送了他一匹黑马。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "这匹黑马在战场上救了霍去病三次，最后一次中箭而死——马用自己的命换了主人的命。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_032", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "隋炀帝开凿大运河时，挖出了一块刻着'隋亡'二字的石碑。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "杨广大怒烧了石碑，但历史的预言最终还是实现了。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_033", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "杜甫在安史之乱中逃难时遇到一个老僧，老僧送了他一碗粥。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "那碗粥让杜甫活了下来，他后来写下了'三吏三别'，记录下了那段历史。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_034", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "刘备三顾茅庐时，在诸葛亮的草庐中发现了一幅没有画完的江山图。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "诸葛亮后来为刘备绘制的'隆中对'战略，就是那幅江山图的完整版。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_historical_035", "genre": "historical", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "光绪皇帝在百日维新前收到了一封匿名信，上面只有一个字——'忍'。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "光绪没有忍，操之过急导致了维新失败，自己被囚禁瀛台。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
